aVAnd there are Muslims, many Muslims out there, who are saying precisely this.
p216
aVAnd they're making this argument wherever they're permitted to make it.
p217
aVBut their governments, needless to say, are relatively threatened by this.
p218
aVAnd for the most part try to stop them from making this argument.
