aVNow what I want to suggest to you is that the reason for hope in this case
p238
aVis that we are on the edge of a real transformation in the Muslim world.
p239
aVAnd that's a transformation in which many sincerely believing Muslims \u2014
p240
aVwho care very, very deeply about their traditions,
p241
aVwho do not want to compromise those values \u2014
p242
aVbelieve, through the malleability of the technology of democracy
