aVfor example, in the regulatory context \u2014 of what democracy produces.
p252
aVIt will also not look exactly the way either the people in this room,
p253
aVor Muslims out in the rest of the world \u2014
p254
aVI don't mean to imply there aren't Muslims here, there probably are \u2014
p255
aVconceptualize Islam.
p256
aVIt will be transformative of Islam as well.
p257
